data.description: New opportunities in the ever popular Silver Canyon subdivision!  A 2 story turn-key residence within the coveted Northside School District.  An open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half bathrooms and a living/family room on each floor. A large amount of natural lighting fills the kitchen/dining room combo, which is large enough to serve the whole family and then some.  Located near major shopping and grocery hotspots, schools, and with quick access to major highway routes. Out back you will find a patio perfect for coffee in the morning doubling as grilling/seating area to entertain guests.      Refrigerator and water softener included.
